entries.s_13: You know I really don't have time. If you are looking for work check out the Lucky Despot. They always have work for people desperate enough.
entries.s_39: I understand that the Lucky Despot has the loosest games in town. Also someone looking for work can find something to do there as well.
entries.s_41: We do this fast. I don't want to know you, and you definitely don't want to know me.
entries.s_42: So show me where Ind's place is.
entries.s_43: Lets get this right. I am not going to show you anything. You are going to go to these coordinates that I am uploading to your datapad. Get it?
entries.s_47: Because I don't want anyone to see me. How dumb are you? Ready? I am updating your datapad. Off you go.
entries.s_48: Well you have more guts that I have. That was a very dangerous game you played with Ind and Kavas.
